--- RESULT ---
All 6 pages are built and ready in `demos/a-neon-cyberpunk/`:

| File | Page | Key Features |
|------|------|------|
| `index.html` | Homepage | Glitch hero, animated gradient mesh, category pills, 6 product cards, 12 brand tiles, news, stats banner |
| `search.html` | Search/Filters | Sticky sidebar with brand accordion, dual-range price slider, featured checkboxes, rating toggle, 12-card grid, active filter chips |
| `brands.html` | Brands Directory | Category filter tabs, 32+ Mobiles brands, 128+ Auto brands, Laptops/TVs sections, glass cards with initials |
| `product.html` | Product Detail | iPhone 16 Pro Max showcase — 6-card specs grid, collapsible `<details>` sections, AI review with pros/cons, vendor cards, related products |
| `compare.html` | Compare | 4 product selector slots, side-by-side specs table with "winner" highlights, auto-generated comparison summary |
| `news.html` | Tech News | 9 article cards (3-per-row grid), trending sidebar with numbered list, category tabs |

**Design features across all pages:**
- Neon Cyberpunk theme (#0a0e1a base, #00f0ff cyan, #ff00ff magenta)
- Glass cards with `backdrop-filter: blur(12px)`, pulsing cyan borders, scanline overlays
- Orbitron headings + Inter body text (Google Fonts)
- Cyber grid background (50px grid lines)
- Glitch text animation on homepage hero
- IntersectionObserver scroll-triggered animations (alternating left/right)
- Mobile responsive with hamburger menu
- `prefers-reduced-motion` support
- All pages cross-linked with relative paths
